==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bolas
<hw>Bo"las</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. sing. & pl.</pos>
<ety>[Sp.]</ety> <def>A kind of missile weapon consisting of one, two,
or more balls of stone, iron, or other material, attached to the ends of
a leather cord; -- used by the Gauchos of South America, and others, for
hurling at and entangling an animal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bold</ent>⟦br⟧
